  <span id="freeText11629518233881030853" style="display:none">A old Victorian house lovingly restored by Elliott is now home to him and his new bride, Gemma.  Life is beautiful.  Ah, time for Elliott to meet the in-laws.  They had been living in France and are currently without a place to call home.  Mom, Pop, and Sis are invited to stay for the nonce while they find a place of their own.  This segues all too quickly into a nightmare.  The family visitors turn into something more akin to squatters, rude, nasty, and possibly dangerous.  Did I mention the home is located on Cuckoo Lane?  Have a care as to whom you invite into your home.  Better yet, cut your losses and don't extend the invitation at all.</span>
