  <span id="freeText16518575790479105686" style="display:none">4.5! My second by Mark Edwards, &amp; it didn’t disappoint! He’s really good at coming at these thrillers from a new angle.. They feel fresh &amp; completely new. I also like the way he develops his characters. I can picture them, I mean I “know” these people by the end of the book! For me, Because She Loves Me (the first of his that i recently read) came out on top, but I think it’s really just a personal preference. Certain people in this 1, &amp; their actions were SO frustrating!! But then, it’s all part of “the fun” of a good story, right?😡🤣🤣</span>
