  <span id="freeText8022723145349577260" style="display:none">Wow, Elliot's in-laws are the stuff nightmares are made of. I thought the book began a little slowly but the intensity escalates steadily until it reaches it's explosive end.<br /><br />This is my first book by Mark Edwards but it is certainly not my last.</span>
